


tfs_chdir(3)          Transtech File System          tfs_chdir(3)



NAME
     tfs_chdir - Change current directory.

SYNOPSYS
     #include <tfs.h>

     int tfs_chdir( int pid, char *path )

ARGUMENTS
     int pid
          Process ID of the logical process.

     char *path
          Name of a directory.

DESCRIPTION
     The directory specified by path is made the  current  direc-
     tory of this logical process.

RETURNS
     Returns zero on success and -1 on  error.   tfs_errno  indi-
     cates the nature of the error.

































